description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Minute Gentle BEGINNERS HIIT Workout | The Body Coach TV' from the channel The Body Coach TV by Joe Wicks.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: 15 moves | 30 seconds work | 30 seconds rest

March on the spot
Side stars
Butt kick punches
Sumo squats
Knee smashes
Reverse lunge/step back arms to sky
Side lunges
Straight punches
Running man
Squat lateral kicks
Jog on the spot
Sumo squat pulse and stand
High plank
Lateral floor touches
Climb the rope
